                            <comment id="14618221" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 8 Jul 2015 08:35:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added a test to trunk (currently ignored): &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1689810&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1689810&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14618298" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 8 Jul 2015 09:41:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Updated test in trunk: &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1689828&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1689828&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14618353" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 8 Jul 2015 10:24:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed fix and enabled test in trunk: &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1689833&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1689833&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14618469" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 8 Jul 2015 11:47:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Remarks about the problem and the fix: the problem was that the head revision could change between the the calls to doc.isCommitted(rev) and SplitOperations.isGarbage(rev). The change was committed in the meantime and the head revision is updated. This breaks an assumption in SplitOperations that the head revision will reflect the same state about the commit as the previous check with isCommitted(). The fix introduces a happens-before relation between the head revision and the document to split and makes sure the head revision is not newer than any uncommitted change observed in the document.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14618519" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 8 Jul 2015 12:40:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Merged into 1.2 branch: &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1689853&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1689853&lt;/a&gt; and 1.0 branch: &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1689860&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1689860&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
